Description of Tether Wallet

Store, send and receive USDT using a simple app designed and developed by Freewallet team.
Install completely free Tether wallet by Freewallet in few seconds.
•  Login with Email, Facebook, Google+ or mobile phone number;
•  Send USDT to almost any altcoin address;
•  Top up the wallet with almost any coin and receive USDT;
•  Coins are stored in Cold storage;
•  App is secured and supported;
•  Real-time USDT price and charts;
•  Balance in fiat currencies;
•  Restore wallet from any device;
•  PIN code and Fingerprint Login;
•  QR Code Support;
•  Optional email confirmation for all transactions;
•  Direct link to USDT block explorer in transactions details;
•  Email notifications about balance changes;
•  Share your wallet address via Twitter, Facebook, email and more;
•  Multiple language support, including Chinese, German, French, Spanish, Russian and more;
•  2-factor authentication;
•  Impeccable 24/7 customer service;
•  Simple and beautiful Freewallet interface.
If you are into Tether trading — use integrated cryptocurrency exchange to convert USDT to almost any coin.
Freewallet is a professional contribution to the cryptocurrency community. It’s developed to bring simplicity to the future of money allowing users to familiarize themselves with popular cryptocurrencies.

Description of Phone Clone

Free to use, completely wireless, easy four-step-migration & ultra-fast speed using local hotspot.
Transfer contacts, messages, photos, videos, music & apps from your old Android to your new Huawei Smartphone.
Transfer contacts, photos & videos from your iPhone to your new Huawei Smartphone.
Even more transfer capabilities from Huawei to Huawei Smartphones: Transfer contacts, messages, photos, videos, music, apps & app data, settings, alarms, memos, browser bookmarks & phone layout.
Update description:
1 Completely new interface,more convenient operation;
